<|vision_start|><|image_pad|><|vision_end|>
Write a detailed description of the given image.
qa_pairs.reasoning_text:
1. The image features a woman with shoulder-length, wavy auburn hair and striking blue eyes, looking directly at the camera with a concerned or startled expression.  
2. She wears a light beige trench coat with a visible collar and a decorative button, suggesting a stylish yet practical outfit for a cool day.  
3. Behind her, a red door with a white sign reading “Hull & Partners” indicates she is standing outside a professional office or business establishment.  
4. A potted plant with green foliage sits beside the door, adding a touch of nature to the urban setting, while a dark staircase is visible to the right.  
5. The lighting casts soft shadows on her face and coat, enhancing the scene’s naturalistic tone and suggesting it was filmed during golden hour or under bright daylight.  

<final> The image portrays a woman in a beige trench coat standing before a red door labeled “Hull & Partners,” with a potted plant nearby and a staircase visible in the background, all under natural lighting. </final>
